      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that slips between gears. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable dents and rust patches, while the interior requires a deep clean and has several torn seats. This would be an ideal project car for someone with mechanical expertise or could serve as a source for parts.",
