    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road with this dependable ride! It\u2019s a solid, honest vehicle that has seen some life but still has plenty of miles left to offer. While it shows some expected wear and tear, it remains a functional and practical choice for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver at a great value. Perfect for someone who appreciates character and a car that gets the job done!",
