      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While it remains mechanically sound and has been regularly serviced, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings. The interior is clean but has minor wear on the driver's seat and some scuffs on the plastic trim. It is a solid, honest car that starts up every time and is ready for its next owner.",
