    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single blemish to be found. It drives incredibly smooth and is just waiting for a new home. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to believe how clean it is. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
