    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative maintenance including a dual-VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement using ACL bearings. The chassis is exceptionally tight, benefiting from a proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry featuring polyurethane bushings. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via the original M-Variable limited-slip differential. The exterior finish exhibits zero orange peel or clear coat failure, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A turn-key example for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
