      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows zero signs of wear; the paint maintains a deep, mirror-like luster, and the interior remains as fresh as the day it was delivered, with crisp leather bolsters and flawless trim. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at the original dealership, with a complete, organized history included. Driven only in fair weather and never subjected to the elements, this vehicle offers a pristine driving experience for the most discerning collector or enthusiast. It is, without exaggeration, the finest example of its kind currently available.",
      "price": 48900.0,
